data.title: Genetic and environmental contributions to the association between ADHD and affective problems in early childhood
data.meta_description: Few twin studies have explored the relative contribution of genetic and environmental factors to the association between attention deficit hyperactivity disorder (ADHD) and affective problems, and no study has focused on preschool children.
